  "stem": "<p>If <i>m</i> &minus; <i>y</i> is a factor of the expression &minus;<i>y</i>&sup2; + (1/37)<i>n</i><i>m</i>&sup2;, where <i>n</i> and <i>m</i> are constants and <i>m</i> &gt; 0, what is the value of <i>n</i>?</p>",
